fr.n7.stl.tam.ast

Interface TAMFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TAMFactoryImpl

    public interface TAMFactory
    Factory to build abstract syntax tree nodes for the TAM language.

      • createReturn

        TAMInstruction createReturn(int _keep,
                            int _remove)
        Build a TAM Return instruction AST node whose execution will pop a memory chunk of the provided _keep size then will pop a call frame from the stack, then will pop a second memory chunk from the stack of the provided _remove size, restore the various registers from the call frame and push the first chunk on the stack.
        Parameters:
        _keep - : The size of the memory chunk that is copied from the top of the stack before removing the execution frame from the call stack, and copied back to the top of the stack after removing the execution frame.
        _remove - : The size of the memory chunk that is removed with the execution frame.
        Returns:
        A TAM Return instruction AST node.
